Captain, you took the first step, the biggest step, and I will not let you ignore that. It was a very big step. Like I have been saying, this site has it's own magic, or karma, or whatever you want to call it, but it works it strange aura on everyone sooner or later, and the result is peace. Peace and understanding.<br><br>
I know &quot;of&quot; your pain and anger, but not of it truly. No one but you can. I can empathize, sympathize, but not fully walk in your shoes. To say I could is a lie.<br><br>
Could it be that our of our ranting and raving, sticks and stones, we have found the middle of the stream? Is the water running cold and clear or is this a dream?  What power lurks here, stuns the mind and encourages the heart.  Like the strings of a lute, each note is another step of reconciliation, of understanding, of reaching mid stream and finding peace, and brotherhood.<br><br>
Our &quot;tribes&quot; are so different, yet our message is so similiar. I am totally blown away by the latest interactions between us.  Maybe we can be the beacon for others to come home to.  I know many watch, many read, only a few post. Let them learn that all things are possible.<br><br>
Even your mystical Inner Circle and my skeptical ravings, have their place, when the intent is honorable, and the heart is true.  <br><br>
Keep talking to me Ed. Keep the fire burning. I will do the same. (though it is late and my yawns grow longer)<br><br>
doc spatz
